features:
  - same game mechanics as flappy bird  
    - tap screen = character goes up on the screen
    - character is constantly falling -> tapping to keep character from crashing down
    - hiting a pipe = fail
    - charcter doesn't move horizontally, pipes coming from top and bottom of the
        screen slide to the direction of the character for the visual of moving
  - differend 'bird' types / skins
    - character can encounter a skin mid-game -> auto changes charaacter's skin
  - background - campus or custom options
  - to win the player must fly between 100 sets of pipes/ obstacles
